Sainsbury's na shirin saka hannun jari a kasuwar kayan kwalliya a Burtaniya
Sainsbury's na son yin gine-ginen kwalliya kamar gidajen kasuwanci don yin gasa da jerin kayayyakin kwalliya na Boots, Superdrug da Debenhams.
Wannan babban saka hannun jari ne na £2.8bn a kasuwar kwalliyar Burtaniya, wadda ke ci gaba da bunkasa yayin da tallace-tallace a fannin kayan kwalliya da kayan gida ke raguwa.
Ana zuba jari a kayan kwalliya a lokacin da manyan kantuna suke neman yadda za su cika wuraren da ake ajiyewa a kan gado da aka yi amfani da su a dā kamar talabijin da bututun ƙarfe da kuma kayan gida.
