Girgizar ƙasa da tsunami a Indonesia sun kashe ɗaruruwan mutane, kuma yawan mutanen da suka mutu suna ƙaruwa
Akalla mutane 384 ne suka mutu kuma mutane da yawa sun mutu a lokacin da manyan raƙuman ruwa suka kai ga rairayin bakin teku a lokacin da girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi da tsunami suka addabi tsibirin Sulawesi, a ƙasar Indonesia, a ranar Asabar, hukumomi sun ce.
A ranar Jumma'a, daruruwan mutane sun taru a wani biki a garin Palu a bakin teku sa'ad da raƙuman ruwa suka kai ga mita shida a bakin teku a yamma, kuma raƙuman ruwa sun halaka duk abin da ya hana su yin hakan, kuma mutane da yawa sun mutu.
Tsunami ya biyo bayan girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin 7.5.
'Sa'ad da ake fuskantar barazanar tsunami a jiya, mutane suna ci gaba da yin ayyukan da suke yi a bakin rairayin bakin teku, ba su gudu ba, sun zama wadanda aka kashe,' in ji Sutopo Purwo Nugroho, kakakin hukumar hana kawo bala'i ta Indonesia (BNPB) a wani taron da aka yi a Jakarta.
"Tsunami ba ta zo da kanta ba, ta ɗauki motoci, da tarkuna, da gidaje, ta kai ga dukan abin da ke kan ƙasa", in ji Nugroho.
Ya ce wasu mutane da suke ƙoƙarin tserewa sun hau itace kuma sun tsira.
An kwashe mutane 16,700 zuwa cibiyoyi 24 a birnin Pal.
Hotunan da hukumar ta wallafa sun nuna gine-gine da shaguna da yawa da suka lalace, gadaje da ke ɓoye da kuma masallaci da ke kewaye da ruwa.
A ranar Asabar, an ci gaba da yin girgizar ƙasa a wannan garin.
An yi girgizar ƙasa da yawa a yankin da ke da mazauna miliyan 2.4 a ƙasar.
Hukumar tantancewa da kuma amfani da fasaha ta Indonesia (BPPT) ta bayyana a cikin wata sanarwa cewa makamashin da aka saki daga mummunan girgizar ƙasa ta ranar Juma'a ya ninka makamashin da aka jefa a lokacin yakin duniya na biyu a Hiroshima da kusan sau 200.
Hukumar ta ce tsunami na iya ƙara yawan birnin da ke bakin wani gaɓar gaɓar teku mai tsawo.
Nugroho ya bayyana cewa an yi mummunan lalacewa kuma ya ce dubban gidaje, asibitoci, gidajen kasuwanci da otal-otal sun rushe.
Ya ce an sami wasu daga cikin waɗanda aka kashe a ƙarƙashin rushewar gine-gine, kuma ya ce mutane 540 ne suka ji rauni kuma 29 sun ɓace.
Nugroho ya ce, asarar rayuka da kuma lalacewar na iya zama mafi girma a yankin Donggala, wanda ke da nisan mil 300 daga arewacin Palau, inda ya fi kusa da tsakiyar girgizar ƙasa.
A cewar Nugroho, an gurgunta hanyoyin sadarwa kuma babu wani bayani daga Donggala.
