A gaba ɗaya, kashi 68 cikin ɗari na ɗaliban da suka yi nazarin yaren waje sun sami mafi girma a matsayin A.
Bayanai daga makarantun da ke cikin rukunin SCIS 74 sun nuna cewa kashi 72 cikin ɗari na ɗaliban sun sami mafi girma A a yaren Mandarin, kashi 72 cikin ɗari a yaren Jamus, kashi 69 cikin ɗari a yaren Faransa, da kuma kashi 63 cikin ɗari a yaren Mutanen Espanya.
