Taron Trump a West Virginia, tashar YouTube
Shugaba Donald Trump ya kaddamar da jerin taron neman zaben a Wheeling, West Virginia.
Wannan ne taro na farko da Trump ya shirya a mako mai zuwa, wanda ya hada da tsayawa a wurare masu alaƙa kamar Tennessee da Mississippi.
Bayan an yi watsi da zaben dan takararsa a kotun koli, Trump na shirin gina goyon baya ga zaben na tsakiya (Midterms) mai zuwa, saboda 'yan Republican na fuskantar rashin iko a zaben a watan Nuwamba.
A wane lokaci ne taron Trump zai faru a West Virginia a yau, kuma a ina za ku iya kallon taron a kan layi?
Taron Trump a Wheeling, West Virginia, yana zuwa a karfe 7:00 na yammacin yau, Asabar, 29 ga Satumba, 2018.
Za ku iya kallon taron Trump a West Virginia a layi a ƙasa, ta hanyar watsa shirye-shiryen YouTube.
Ana iya ganin Trump zai yi magana game da sauraron da ake yi wa dan takarar a kotun koli, Bret Kavanaugh, wanda ya yi matukar damuwa game da zargin cin zarafin jima'i, yayin da majalisar dattijai ta jinkirta amincewa da shi har mako guda yayin da FBI ke gudanar da bincike.
Amma babban burin wannan taron shine taimaka wa 'yan Republican da za su sake samun iko a lokacin babban zaben Nuwamba.
Rahoton da Reuters ta ba da ya nuna cewa taro biyar da za a yi a makon gobe za su yi nufin tada hankalin masu sa kai da masu goyon baya, domin 'yan Republican suna ƙoƙarin karewa da kuma faɗaɗa rinjayen da suke da su a Majalisar Dattawa da kuma Majalisar Dattijai.
"Sarrafawa a kan majalisa tana da matukar muhimmanci ga tsarinsa, wanda a lokacin da za a fara zaben da aka yi a kan hanya, shugaban zai yi tafiya zuwa jihohi da yawa", wani mai magana da yawun Trump ya shaida wa Reuters, wanda ya ƙi a nada shi.
A yau, taron da ake yi a Wesbanco Arena a Wheeling zai iya jawo hankalin masu sauraro daga Ohio da Pennsylvania kuma ya jawo hankalin kafofin watsa labarai daga Pittsburgh, West Virginia Metro News ta ruwaito.
Trump zai ziyarci West Virginia a ranar Asabar a karo na biyu a cikin wata daya da ya gabata, jihar da ya lashe zaben da sama da kashi 40 cikin dari a shekarar 2016.
Trump na neman goyon bayan dan takarar jam'iyyar Republican ga majalisar dattijai a West Virginia, Patrick Morrissey, wanda ya samu karbuwa a zaben.
"Ba shi da kyau ga Morrissey cewa shugaban ya zo ya ba shi fifiko a cikin binciken", in ji Simon Haeder, masanin siyasa a Jami'ar West Virginia, a cewar Reuters.
