'Yan Rangers sun sha wahala a wani zagaye na baƙin ciki a wasan waje, lokacin da harbin Dolly Mengu ya yi wa tawagar Steven Gerrard da ta yi rashin nasara hukuncin da ya yi a Livingstone.
Gidan Ibrox ya yi kokarin samun nasarar da suka samu a waje tun daga nasarar 4:1 a St Johnstone a watan Fabrairu, amma tawagar Gary Holt ta kawo Gerrard na biyu ne kawai a cikin wasanni 18 a matsayin manajan, kuma ta bar tawagarsa ta kasance a matsayi na maki 8 daga shugabannin Ladbrokes Premiership, wato Hearts.
Menga ya ci kwallaye bakwai kafin rabin lokaci kuma Rangers da ke da rashin wahayi ba su zo kusa da daidaitawa ba.
