Kasar Sin ta ce ta samu karuwar kashi 14 cikin 100 a yawan mutanen da ke dauke da cutar HIV da Aids.
Masu kula da lafiya sun ce mutane fiye da 820,000 ne suka kamu da cutar a ƙasar.
A cikin kwata na biyu na 2018 kadai, an samu karin karin karin mutane 40,000.
Yawancin sababbin cututtuka sun kasance na jima'i, wanda ya canza daga baya.
A wasu sassa na ƙasar Sin, an yi amfani da jini don yaɗa cutar HIV da sauri.
Amma, adadin mutanen da suka kamu da cutar HIV ta wannan hanyar ya ragu zuwa kusan sifili, kamar yadda jami'an kiwon lafiya na kasar Sin suka ce a wani taro a lardin Yunnan.
Amma a cikin shekara guda, adadin mutanen da ke da HIV da AIDS a ƙasar Sin ya ƙaru da mutane 100,000.
Cutar HIV ta hanyar jima'i babbar matsala ce a cikin al'ummar LGBT na kasar Sin.
An yi watsi da jima'i a kasar Sin a shekara ta 1997, amma har yanzu ana nuna bambanci ga LGBT.
Saboda ra'ayoyin da suka nuna cewa ƙasar tana da kyau, binciken ya nuna cewa kashi 70 zuwa 90 cikin 100 na maza da suka yi jima'i da namiji sun auri wata mace a ƙarshe.
Yawancin cututtuka na cututtuka sun fito ne daga rashin kariya ta jima'i a cikin waɗannan dangantaka.
Tun daga shekara ta 2003, gwamnatin Sin ta yi alkawarin samun cikakken damar yin amfani da maganin HIV a ƙoƙarin magance wannan matsalar.
Maxine Waters ta musanta cewa ma'aikacinta zai bar bayanan sanatocin GOP su shiga, ta yi ta sukar karya mai hatsari da kuma ka'idojin ta'addanci
A ranar Asabar, 'yar majalisa ta Amurka Maxine Waters ta yi watsi da zargin da ake yi mata cewa wani ma'aikacinta ya aika bayanan sirri na wasu 'yan majalisar Republican na Amurka zuwa shafin Wikipedia na 'yan majalisar.
'Yan Democrat a Los Angeles sun ce sun yi zargin cewa masana masu zurfin-dama ne suka yi hakan kuma sun yi amfani da shafukan intanet.
"Karya, ƙarya da kuma wasu ƙazanta ƙarya", in ji Waters a wata sanarwa a shafinta na Twitter.
An bayyana cewa, bayanan da aka bayar sun ƙunshi adiresoshin gida da kuma lambobin waya na Sanatocin Amirka Lindsey Graham na Kudancin Carolina da kuma Mike Lee da Orrin Hatch, duka biyu daga Utah.
Bayanai sun bayyana a yanar gizo a ranar Alhamis, wani ba a san shi ba ya bayyana su a kan Capitol Hill yayin da ake sauraron majalisar dattawa game da zargin cin zarafin jima'i da ake yi wa dan takarar Kotun Koli, Brett Kavanaugh.
Bayan wasu sanatoci uku sun yi wa Kavanaugh tambayoyi, an yi watsi da bayanan.
Shafukan tsaro kamar su Gateway Pundit da RedState sun sanar da cewa adiresoshin IP da ke gano tushen ɓarnar suna da alaƙa da ofishin Waters kuma sun ba da bayani game da wani ma'aikacin Waters, Hill ya sanar.
Waters ta ci gaba da cewa, "Wannan zargin da ba a tabbatar da shi ba ƙarya ne kuma ƙarya ce gaba ɗaya.
Wani ma'aikaci na da aka lalata da shi, da kuma bayanansa da kuma amincinsa saboda irin wannan zargi na karya da kuma na karya, ba shi da alhakin wannan bayanan.
Wannan zargin da ba a tabbatar da shi ba, ƙarya ne da ƙarya.
Sanarwar Waters ta yi saurin samun karɓan rahoto a kan layi, daga cikin waɗanda tsohon sakataren labarai na fadar White House, Ari Fleischer ya yi.
"Kin amincewa da ita yana cike da fushi", in ji Fleischer.
Wannan yana nuna cewa ba ta da halin da ya dace ta zama 'yar majalisa.
Idan an zargi wani da wani abu da bai yi ba, kada ka yi fushi.
Bai kamata ya yi tawaye ba.
Bai kamata ya yi tambaya game da dalilin da ya sa ake tuhumar da shi ba.
Dole ne ya kasance mai salama da daidaitacce.
Fleischer ya kwatanta yadda Waters ya amsa da suka yi wa Alkalin Kavanaugh da 'yan Democrat suka zarge shi da cewa ya yi fushi sosai a lokacin sauraronsa a ranar Alhamis.
Omar Navarro, dan takarar jam'iyyar Republican da ke neman takarar Waters a zaben fidda gwani, ya kuma bayyana ra'ayinsa a shafinsa na Twitter.
"Idan gaskiya ne, to, babban abu ne", ya rubuta.
A cikin wata sanarwa, Waters ta ce ofishinta ta sanar da hukumomin da ke da alaka da shari'ar da ake tuhuma game da zargin karya.
Ta ci gaba da cewa, za mu tabbatar da cewa an gano masu aikata laifin kuma za su yi wa mutane shari'a don ayyukansu da ke da lahani ga dukan ma'aikatanmu.
Johnny English ya sake shiga cikin wani fim din da ya nuna wani ɗan leƙen asiri da Rowan Atkins
A yau, yana da kyau a nemi a cikin kowane sabon fim na Burtaniya don yin tunani game da Brexit, kuma wannan ya shafi wannan reincarnation na wasan kwaikwayo na wasan kwaikwayo tare da Johnny English  wanda aka fara a 2003 tare da Johnny English kuma ya dawo da rai a 2011 tare da Johnny English yana dawowa.
Shin za a yi wani ba'a game da yadda muka gaza a matsayin sabon kayan fitarwa na kasa?
Ko ta yaya, Johnny English da bai da ƙwarewa da kuma saurin nunawa ya sake samun damar yin lalata da kome  kuma sunansa ya nuna cewa shi mai karimci ne wanda aka tsara musamman don masu sauraron da ba Turanci ba.
Hakika, shi ne wani ɗan asiri marar wayo wanda duk da cewa yana da ƙarancin ƙwarewar da ake bukata don yin kyau, yana da ɗan ƙaramin abu daga Clouseau, daga Mr Bean, kuma daga mutumin da ya ba da gudummawa ta musamman ga waƙar farko ta Chariots of Fire a bikin buɗe gasar Olympics ta London a shekara ta 2012.
A baya, an fara yin fim dinsa ne na wani matafiyi na duniya da kuma wani mutum mai ban mamaki da Atkinson ya yi a wani tallan talabijin da aka manta da shi a Barclaycard, yana barin rudani a ko'ina.
A cikin wannan kasada ta ƙarshe da Johnny English ya yi, za a iya samun lokaci ko biyu masu kyau.
Na ji daɗin ganin Johnny English yana zuwa jirgin sama da kayan ƙarni na tsakiya kuma ya yi amfani da jirgi mai saukar ungulu don ya kai shi saman kwalkwali.
Wannan yana nuna cewa Atkinson yana da baiwa ga wasan kwaikwayo na zahiri, amma ban dariya yana da ɗan ƙarami da kuma ɗan ban mamaki, musamman ma lokacin da manyan kamfanonin fim kamar 007 da Mission Impossible kansu suka riga sun ba da wasan kwaikwayo a matsayin wani ɓangare na su.
Abin dariya ya fi dacewa da yara fiye da manya, kuma a ganina, ba a taɓa ganin abubuwan da Johnny English ya yi ba kamar yadda Atkinson ya yi a cikin Mr. Bean.
A halin yanzu, labarin fim din ya nuna cewa Birtaniya tana cikin matsala mai tsanani.
Wani dan gwanin kwamfuta ya shiga cikin wani rukunin yanar gizo na 'yan leken asiri na Birtaniya kuma, don tsoratar da wani jami'in da ke aiki, Kevin Eldon, wanda ya yi rashin alheri ya yi wani abu mai ban mamaki, ya bayyana ainihin dukkan jami'an Birtaniya a yankin.
Wannan shi ne ƙarshen firaministan, wanda shi ne mai girman kai da kuma mai gwagwarmaya, wanda ya riga ya kusan rushewa saboda rashin shahararren siyasa: Emma Thompson tana yin abin da ta iya tare da wani mai kama da Theresa May, amma ba ta da wani abu da za ta yi aiki da shi a cikin labarin.
Masu ba ta shawara a kan labarai sun gaya mata cewa idan an yi wa kowane ɗan leƙen asiri da ke aiki ya ci amanarsu, dole ne ta kira wani ya yi ritaya.
A wannan lokacin, Johnny English da kansa ya zo, wanda a yau yake aiki a matsayin darektan wata babbar ma'aikata, wanda ke koyar da darussan sirri game da yadda za a zama ɗan leƙen asiri: a nan akwai wasu gags masu ban sha'awa kamar yadda English ke koyar da darussan leƙen asiri kamar School of Rock.
Sa'an nan kuma Inglis ya koma Whitehall don yin taron gaggawa kuma ya sadu da tsohon dan wasan Bough, wanda aka sake buga shi da Ben Miller.
Bough yanzu namiji ne da ya yi aure, yana da alaƙa da wani kwamandan jirgin ruwa mai rauni, wanda Vicki Pepperdine ta yi baƙin ciki.
Saboda haka Batman da Robin, masanan masifu a cikin sirrin sarautarsa, sun koma cikin filin wasa kuma sun yi magana game da kyakkyawan femme fatale, Ophelia Bullet a cikin gabatarwar Olga Kurylenk.
A halin yanzu, Firayim Minista tana fuskantar wata masifa mai ban mamaki ta hanyar yin amfani da fasaha mai ban sha'awa wanda ke da'awar cewa zai iya magance matsalolin kwamfuta na Birtaniya: Jason Volta mai ban tsoro Jake Lacy.
English da Bough sun fara jerin abubuwan da ba su da kyau: sun yi sutura a matsayin masu hidima kuma sun ƙone gidan cin abinci na Faransa mai haske; sun kawo rikici yayin da suka shiga cikin jirgin ruwa mai kayatarwa na Volt; kuma English ya lalata tsarkakakkiyar rashin adalci lokacin da ya yi ƙoƙarin amfani da na'urar VR don ya san abin da ke cikin gidan Volt.
