Lindsey Graham da John Kennedy sun yi magana a kan shirin 60 Minutes ko binciken FBI akan Kavanaugh zai iya canza ra'ayinsu
Binciken FBI game da zargin da ake yi wa Alkalin Brett Kavanaugh ya hana a kammala zaben nadin shi a kotun koli na akalla mako guda kuma ya yi tambaya ko binciken da hukumar ta gano zai iya rinjayar wasu Sanatocin Republican su janye goyon bayansu.
A wata hira da aka yi a ranar Lahadi, mai gabatar da jawabi a shirin 60 Minutes, Scott Pelley, da Sanatocin Republican John Kennedy da Lindsey Graham, sun tambayi ko FBI za ta iya gano wani abu da zai sa su canja ra'ayinsu.
