Wakilan ƙasashen da ke goyon bayan Grace sun kwatanta El Salvador da Honduras da kuma Guatemala, inda yawan masu neman mafaka daga Amirka suka fito, a matsayin al'ummai da ke fuskantar manyan matsalolin gangami da kuma tashin hankali a gida.
Sabon manufar 'yan gudun hijira ta Amurka ta yi watsi da hukuncin da Hukumar Kula da Bukatar Shige da Fice ta 2014 ta yanke wanda ya ba da damar yin neman mafaka ga baƙi da ba a yi musu rajista ba da ke tserewa daga tashin hankali na gida.
A ranar Juma'a, Babban Shari'a na District of Columbia, Karl Racine, ya ce sabon manufar ta yi watsi da dokokin jihar, tarayya da na duniya na shekaru da yawa.
Federal law ya bukaci a yi la'akari da duk aikace-aikacen neman mafaka bisa ga ainihin abubuwan da ake yi da kuma yanayin da ake nema, kuma irin wannan yanke shawara ta keta wannan ka'idar, in ji amicus curiae.
