Jakadan Amurka ya zargi kasar Sin da cin zarafin ta ta hanyar tallatawa
Wata mako bayan da jaridar Sin ta wallafa wani shafi na hudu a cikin jaridar Amirka, yana tallata amfanin cinikayya tsakanin Amurka da China, jakadan Amurka ya zargi kasar Sin da amfani da jaridar Amurka don yada propaganda.
A ranar Laraba, shugaban Amurka Donald Trump ya yi magana game da wani tallan da aka biya na China Daily a cikin Des Moines Register, wata jarida mafi sayarwa a jihar Iowa, bayan ya zargi kasar Sin da yin tsattsauran ra'ayi a zaben Amurka na ranar 6 ga watan Nuwamba.
A cewar jami'an Amurka da suka gaya wa Reuters, zargin da Trump ya yi wa Beijing na kokarin tsoma baki a zaben Amurka wani sabon mataki ne a yakin neman zaben Washington na matsa lamba a kan kasar Sin.
