Wanda ya kirkiro yanar gizo mai suna World Wide Web yana shirin kaddamar da wani sabon intanet don ya fi karfin Google da Facebook
Tim Berners-Lee, wanda ya kirkiro yanar gizo, ya kaddamar da wani shiri na farko da zai yi kokarin yin gasa da Facebook da Amazon da kuma Google.
Wani sabon shiri na wannan sanannen fasaha, mai suna Inrupt, kamfani ne wanda ya samo asali ne daga dandalin Solid na Berners-Lee.
Solid yana ba masu amfani damar yanke shawara ko ana adana bayanan su kuma wanda aka ba da izinin samun damar kowane bayani.
A wata hira da aka yi da Fast Company, Berners-Lee ya yi wa'azi cewa manufar Inrupt ita ce "mulkin duniya".
Ya ce dole ne mu shiga yanzu, game da farawa.
Wannan lokaci ne na tarihi.
Aikace-aikacen da ke amfani da fasaha mai suna Solid yana ba mutane damar ƙirƙirar nasu shagon ajiyar bayanai na kan layi ko POD.
Zai iya ƙunshi jerin sunayen lambobin sadarwa, jerin ayyuka, kalandar, ɗakin karatu na kiɗa da sauran kayan aiki na mutum da na aiki.
Yana kama da Google Drive, Microsoft Outlook, Slack, da Spotify, kuma duk suna samuwa a cikin burauzar guda ɗaya.
Abin da ke da ban sha'awa game da ajiyar bayanan sirri ta kan layi shi ne cewa mai amfani ne kawai ke yanke shawara ko wane ne zai sami damar yin amfani da kowane irin bayani.
Wannan shi ne abin da kamfanin ya kira "Ƙarfafa ikon mutum ta hanyar bayanai".
Inrupt ya ce manufar kamfanin ita ce ya kawo albarkatu, tsari da kuma ƙwarewar da za su sa Solid ya kasance a wurin kowa.
A halin yanzu, Berners-Lee, Bruce, dandalin tsaro da IBM ta saya, da wasu masu tasowa na cikin gida da aka yi hayar su yi aiki a kan aikin, da kuma ƙungiyar masu ba da kyauta.
Tun daga wannan makon, masu fasaha a duk faɗin duniya sun fara gina nasu aikace-aikacen da ba a rarraba su ba ta amfani da kayan aikin da ke cikin shafin yanar gizon Inrupt.
Berners-Lee ya ce shi da tawagarsa ba sa tattaunawa da Facebook da Google game da ko za su yi wani canji na gaba daya wanda zai rushe tsarin kasuwancin su gaba daya a daren nan ko a'a.
Ba mu nemi izini daga gare su ba.
A wani rubutu da ya wallafa a shafin Medium a ranar Asabar, Berners-Lee ya rubuta cewa, "Mishin Inrupt shi ne samar da makamashi na kasuwanci da kuma tsarin halittu wanda zai taimaka wajen kare mutuncin da kuma ingancin sabon shafin yanar gizon da aka gina akan dandalin Solid".
A shekara ta 1994, Berners-Lee ya canja Intanet ta wajen kafa Ƙungiyar Yanar Gizo ta Duniya a Cibiyar Fasaha ta Massachusetts.
A cikin 'yan watannin nan, Berners-Lee ya zama babbar murya a tattaunawar tsaka tsaki na yanar gizo.
Har ila yau, bayan Inrupt ya fara aiki, Berners-Lee ya kasance mai kafa da kuma darektan World Wide Web Consortium, Web Foundation da Open Data Institute.
"Ina ganin zamani na yanar gizo mai zuwa da kyakkyawan fata", in ji Berners-Lee.
