An sake jinkirta sabon jirgin saman Jamus
Kafofin watsa labarai na gida sun ruwaito cewa an ƙaddamar da sabon jirgin ruwan jirgin ruwa na Jamus a cikin 2014 don maye gurbin tsoffin jiragen ruwa na Cold War, amma ba za a yi hakan ba har zuwa shekara mai zuwa saboda rashin tsari da kuma yawan farashin.
A cewar jaridar Die Zeit, an jinkirta shigar da jirgin Rheinland-Pfalz, wanda ke jagorantar sabon jirgin ruwan Baden-Württemberg, zuwa farkon rabin 2019.
A shekarar 2014, an shirya cewa za a shiga cikin rundunar jiragen ruwa, amma an samu matsala a kan wannan babban shiri bayan an kawo shi.
Jirgin ruwa hudu na Baden-Württemberg da Navy ta ba da umarni a shekara ta 2007 za su zo don maye gurbin tsofaffin jiragen ruwa na Bremen.
An san cewa za su ƙunshi manyan makamai masu linzami, wasu makamai masu linzami da na'urori masu linzami, da kuma wasu fasahohin ɓoyewa kamar rage hasken radar, infrared da kuma sautin sauti.
Sauran muhimman ayyuka sun haɗa da tsawon lokacin kulawa − ya kamata a iya sanya sabbin jiragen ruwa har tsawon shekaru biyu a waje da tashar jiragen ruwa.
Amma, ana ganin cewa jiragen da suka ba Jamus damar nuna iko a kasashen waje za su zama tsofaffi a lokacin da suka soma aiki, in ji jaridar Die Zeit.
A shekarar da ta shige, an yi magana game da jirgin ruwan F125 da ya faru a lokacin da rundunar sojan ruwa ta Jamus ta ƙi shigar da shi cikin aiki kuma ta mayar da shi zuwa tashar jiragen ruwa ta Blohm & Voss a Hamburg.
Wannan shi ne karo na farko da rundunar jiragen ruwa ta ba da jirgin ga mai ginin bayan an kawo shi.
Ba a san dalilan da suka sa aka koma ba, amma kafofin watsa labarai na Jamus sun ambaci wasu manyan kuskuren software da na'urori masu aiki da suka sa jirgin ya zama ba zai iya amfani da shi ba a lokacin da ake amfani da shi a aikin yaƙi.
Ƙarancin software na musamman yana da muhimmanci domin jiragen ruwa na Baden-Württemberg za su yi aiki da ma'aikatan jiragen ruwa na kimanin 120 - rabin ma'aikatan jiragen ruwa na Bremen.
An kuma nuna cewa jirgin yana da nauyi mai yawa wanda ke rage ƙarfinsa kuma yana iyakance ikon jirgin ruwa don ƙara haɓakawa na gaba.
Jirgin ruwan Rheinland-Pfalz mai nauyin ton 7 000 yana da nauyi sau biyu na irin wannan rukunin jiragen da Jamus ta yi amfani da su a lokacin Yaƙin Duniya na Biyu.
Ƙari ga matsalar rashin kayan aiki, an yi amfani da kuɗin da ake kashewa don yin aikin - har da koyar da ma'aikatan.
An ce ta kai dala biliyan 3.1 (dolar Amurka biliyan 3.6) - daga wajen dala biliyan 2.2 na asali.
Matsalolin da ke shafan jiragen ruwa na zamani suna da muhimmanci musamman a cikin kwanan nan, saboda gargaɗin da aka yi cewa sojojin ruwa na Jamus suna raguwa.
A farkon wannan shekara, Hans-Peter Bartels, shugaban kwamitin tsaro na majalisar dokokin Jamus, ya tabbatar da cewa a zahiri, rundunar jiragen ruwa ba ta da jiragen ruwa masu iya yin amfani da su.
Wani wakilin gwamnati ya ce wannan tambayar ta taso a tsawon lokaci saboda an soke tsoffin jiragen ruwa amma ba a samar da wasu jirage masu maye gurbin su ba.
