Girgizar Kasa da Tsunami a Indonesia
Akalla mutane 384 ne suka mutu a girgizar ƙasa da tsunami da suka auku a birnin Palulu da ke ƙasar Indonesia a ranar Juma'a.
Saboda rashin isashen saƙo, jami'an agaji ba su iya samun wani bayani daga ofishin gwamnan Donggala ba, wani yanki da ke arewacin Palau, wanda ya fi kusa da tsakiyar girgizar ƙasa mai karfin 7.5.
An kwashe mutane fiye da 16,000 a Pala bayan da aka yi wa wannan bala'in.
Ga wasu muhimman bayanai game da birnin Palu da kuma birnin Donggala a Sulawesi:
Palu ita ce babban birnin lardin Sulawesi ta tsakiya, wanda ke a ƙarshen ƙuƙwalwar tekun a yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi, tare da kimanin mutane 379,800 a cikin 2017.
A lokacin da girgizar ƙasa da tsunami suka afka wa birnin, ya yi bikin cika shekaru 40.
Donggala wani gari ne da ke da nisan mil 300 a arewa maso yammacin Sulawesi.
A shekara ta 2017, an kiyasta yawan mutanen da ke cikin yankin da ke cikin lardin da ke cikin yankin da ke cikin yankin da ke cikin yankin da ke cikin lardin.
Fishing da kuma noma sune manyan abubuwan da ke tallafawa tattalin arzikin Sulawesi ta tsakiya, musamman yankin Donggala na bakin teku.
Ana yin amfani da nickel a lardin, amma yawanci a Morowali ne, a bakin tekun Sulawesi.
Hukumar kula da bala'i ta Indonesia ta ce tsunami ya auku a birnin Palu da Donggala sau da yawa a cikin shekaru 100 da suka shige.
A shekara ta 1938, tsunami ya kashe mutane fiye da 200 kuma ya lalata ɗaruruwan gidaje a birnin Donggala.
Wata tsunami da ta afku a yammacin birnin Donggala a shekara ta 1996 ta kashe mutane tara.
Indonesia tana cikin tekun Pacific na wuta, kuma tana fuskantar girgizar ƙasa a kai a kai.
Ga wasu manyan girgizar ƙasa da tsunami da suka faru a cikin 'yan shekarun nan:
2004: Wani girgizar ƙasa mai tsanani a yammacin tekun lardin Aceh a arewacin Sumatra, Indonesia, ta jawo tsunami a ranar 26 ga watan Disamba, wanda ya shafi ƙasashe 14, ya kashe mutane 226,000 a gabar tekun Tekun Indiya, fiye da rabin su a Aceh.
2005: A ƙarshen Maris da kuma farkon Afrilu, an yi girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi a yammacin Sumatra.
Daruruwan mutane sun mutu a tsibirin Nias a bakin tekun Sumatra.
2006: Girgizar ƙasa mai karfin awo 6.8 ta afkawa kudancin Java, tsibirin da aka fi yawan jama'a a Indonesia, ta jawo tsunami da ya afkawa kudu da gabar tekun, inda ya kashe kusan mutane 700.
2009: Wani girgizar ƙasa mai karfin awo 7.6 ta afku kusa da Padang, babban birnin lardin West Sumatra.
Mutane fiye da 1,100 ne aka kashe.
2010: Girgizar ƙasa mai karfin awo 7.5 ta afkawa tsibirin Mentawai, a wajen Sumatra, kuma ta jawo tsunami mai tsayi na mita 10, wanda ya halaka ƙauyuka da dama kuma ya kashe mutane kusan 300.
2016: Wani mummunan girgizar ƙasa ya afkawa gwamnatin Pidie Jaya a Aceh, wanda ya haifar da lalacewa da firgici lokacin da ya tunatar da mutane game da lalacewar da ta faru a cikin girgizar ƙasa da tsunami na 2004.
A wannan lokacin, babu tsunami, amma mutane fiye da 100 sun mutu a sakamakon rushewar gine-gine.
2018: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi ta afkawa tsibirin Lombok na Indonesia, inda ta kashe mutane fiye da 500, mafi yawa a arewacin tsibirin.
Girgizar ta lalata dubban gine-gine kuma ta sa dubban masu yawon bude ido su makale a wani lokaci.
