Masu gabatar da kara na tarayya suna neman hukuncin kisa mai wuya ga wani dan ta'addanci a birnin New York
'Yan sandan tarayya a New York suna neman hukuncin kisa ga Sayful Saipov, wanda ake zargi da harin ta'addanci a New York wanda ya kashe mutane takwas. Wannan kisa ce mai wuya da ba a yi ta ba a jihar ba tun 1953.
An ce a ranar 31 ga watan Oktoba, Saipov mai shekara 30 ya yi amfani da motar hayar Home Depot don kai hari a kan titin babur a kan titin West Side a Lower Manhattan ta hanyar buga matafiya da kuma masu hawa keke a kan hanya.
A cewar sanarwar da aka ba da a kudancin New York, don a yi kisa, masu gabatar da kara za su bukaci su nuna cewa Saipov ya kashe mutane takwas da gangan kuma ya yi musu mummunan rauni.
A cikin takardar shari'a, an ba da hukuncin kisa ga waɗannan batutuwan biyu.
Bayan 'yan makonni bayan harin, wata kotu ta gabatar da karar da ta kai ga Saipov, wanda ya hada da tuhuma guda takwas na kisan kai da nufin cin zarafi, wanda yawanci masu gabatar da kara na tarayya ke amfani da su wajen gudanar da ayyukan aikata laifuka, da kuma tuhumar da ake yi wa motoci da lalata motoci.
Masu gabatar da kara sun ce harin ya bukaci "babban shiri da tunani mai sanyi" kuma sun bayyana yadda Saipov ya kai shi a matsayin mummunan, mummunan da kuma munanan.
Saifullo Habibullaevic Saipov ya yi wa dangin Diego Enrique Angelini, Nicholas Cleves, Ann-Laure Decadotte, Darren Drake, Ariel Erli, Hernan Ferruchi, Hernan Diego Mendoza da Alejandro Damian Pagnucca rauni, rauni da asarar, da kuma abokansa, rahoton ya ce.
Biyar daga cikin wadanda aka kashe sun kasance 'yan yawon bude ido ne daga Argentina.
Shekara goma kenan da kotun kudancin New York ta ba da hukuncin kisa.
An yanke wa wanda ake tuhuma, Khalid Barnes, hukuncin kisa a kan kisan wasu masu sayar da miyagun ƙwayoyi biyu, amma a watan Satumba na shekara ta 2009, an yanke masa hukuncin daurin rai a kurkuku.
An yi kisa na ƙarshe a cikin wata shari'a ta tarayya a New York a shekara ta 1953 don Julius da Ethel Rosenbergs. An kashe ma'aurata bayan an yanke musu hukuncin kisa don yin tsinkaye da kuma leken asiri ga Soviet Union a lokacin Cold War shekaru biyu da suka shige.
